# Unit cube centered at the origin (side 1.0).
# Low-poly arena landmark/pillar for Spike A — 12 tris after the encoder
# fan-triangulates the 6 quad faces, vs the teapot's 552, so we can instance
# a whole grid of them under the DS ~2048-poly/frame budget.
# No vn records: bevy_nds_3d_obj fills each face's normal from its geometry,
# giving clean flat-shaded lighting.
o Cube

v -0.5 -0.5 -0.5
v -0.5 -0.5  0.5
v -0.5  0.5 -0.5
v -0.5  0.5  0.5
v  0.5 -0.5 -0.5
v  0.5 -0.5  0.5
v  0.5  0.5 -0.5
v  0.5  0.5  0.5

# Quads wound CCW as seen from outside (front-facing).
f 1 2 4 3
f 5 7 8 6
f 1 5 6 2
f 3 4 8 7
f 1 3 7 5
f 2 6 8 4
